- "Highest overall score across all competitions" means the skater has the highest cumulative score from all their performances.

- "Top 3 skaters from each nation" refers to the skaters ranked 1st, 2nd, and 3rd in their respective nations based on their performance in the competition;
- "Latest competition" refers to the most recent year in the `competitions` table;
